gory:Spanish-language television programs]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Mexican television morning show}}\n{{Unreferenced|date=April 2020}}\n{{Infobox television\n| show_name                = Sale El Sol\n| image                    = Logotipook.png\n| image_size               = 150px\n| genre                    = [[Breakfast television|Morning news/talk]]<br>[[Interview (magazine)|Interview]]\n| creator                  = \n| director                 = \n| presenter                = [[Luz Mar\u00eda Zetina]]<br>Carlos Arenas<br>Paulina Mercado<br>Roberto Carlo<br>\n| theme_music_composer     = \n| opentheme                = \"Sale el Sol\" by N\u00e9bulas\n| endtheme                 = \n| composer                 = \n| country                  = Mexico\n| language                 = Spanish\n| num_seasons              = 4\n| list_episodes            = \n| executive_producer       = \n| producer                 = Andr\u00e9s Tovar<br>(2016-present)<br>Natalia Pereda Fern\u00e1ndez<br>(2019-present)<br>David Ortiz Marquet<br>(2017-2019)<br>Eric Reid<br>(2016-2017)\n| location                 = [[Mexico City]], [[Mexico]]<br>(2016-present)\n| editor                   = \n| camera                   = [[Multi-camera setup|Multi-camera]]\n| runtime                  = 180 minutes (including commercials)\n| company                  = [[Grupo Imagen]]\n| distributor              = \n| network                  = [[Imagen Televisi\u00f3n]]\n| picture_format           = [[1080i]] ([[HDTV]])<br>[[480i]] ([[SDTV]])\n| first_aired              = October 18, 2016\n| last_aired               = present\n| preceded_by              = ''Nuestro D\u00eda''\n| followed_by              = \n| related                  = \n| website                  = http://www.imagentv.com/entretenimiento/sale-el-sol\n| production_website       = \n}}\n\n'''''Sale El Sol''''' ([[English language|English]]: ''The Sun Comes Out'') is a [[Mexican]] [[breakfast television|television daily morning progra